{"tid":1625354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港無得再輸，聽日無論點都要出","createTime":"2019-10-05T06:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T07:31:28.000Z","uid":222569,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ea2876e1c6ba7bd48a94c87e0b63dcd5c5edca","tid":1625354,"uid":222569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:41:11.000Z","msg":"‼️出‼️<br />\n<br />\n再諗深一層, 我覺得緊急蒙面法第一日就話要休息, 好多淺黃唔係太清楚 會以為蒙面法嚇怕好多人而令到以後佢地都唔敢出, 你今日休息係已經間接幫淺黃製造白色恐怖, 咁以後場運場係咪自然會少人?<br />\n<br />\n第一日既印象觀感其實好緊要, 要知道淺黃根本佔香港人大比數, 佢地好多時唔知情況, 見到第一日少人, 以後就好難有人出黎。<br />\n<br />\n被拉近二千手足唔係condom。<br />\n<br />\n大家行出來對，IGNORANCE IS NOT INNOCENT BUT SIN<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日見<br />\n<strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLGPyP0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLGPyP0.jpg&h=090b8961&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4352713484f693f4cf92acc583067f56a8e8a5e3","tid":1625354,"uid":222569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:41:24.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"1745e684fe058f4c0a9c95d6f6b602503eab1646","tid":1625354,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:41:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8e54c9acd5a061793db5f00dee804c9b21a458dd","tid":1625354,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:41:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b98fe9caa317e74a4a86d8e6745f42ee8cbafac5","tid":1625354,"uid":298428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:42:15.000Z","msg":"支持聽日集中300萬<br />\n<br />\n300萬人多安全！<br />\n<br />\n和理非300萬做國際文宣有用！<br />\n<br />\n和理非==》 自己拎遮 遮個大太陽行街好安全！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad9e673bd06ae63f5d3b8b0d498eeeba166b17c","tid":162